  "subject": "[AAI] Schema changes for Cell and Neighbour and Fix package issue in v28 version",
  "commit_message": "[AAI] Schema changes for Cell and Neighbour and Fix package issue in v28 version\n\n- AAI Cell band and Neighbour objects relation-type attributes are added\n- Fix the org.onap.aai.domain.yang package issue in v28 version\n- Reverted schema changes from v27 and add into v28 version again\n\nIssue-ID: AAI-3663\nChange-Id: I69e6425f7d7b04013c832a3d48819a510699627e\nSigned-off-by: nandkishorpatke <nandkishor-laxman.patke@t-systems.com>\n",
